# ─── Frontend env vars ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# All configuration lives in the ROOT .env file (../.env).
# Vite is configured to read from the project root automatically.
# You do NOT need a separate frontend/.env file.
#
# If you still want a local override, create frontend/.env with these vars:
#
# VITE_API_URL=/api
# VITE_MAPBOX_TOKEN=pk.eyJ1IjoiWU9VUl9VU0VSTkFNRSIsImEiOiJZT1VSX1RPS0VOX0hFUkUifQ.XXXXX
